### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/

### Listen event - empty signature returns the "secretkey is empty" path when secret unset
POST http://localhost:8080/api/listenevent
Content-Type: application/json
X-SUMT-Signature: t=1700000000,v1=deadbeef

{
  "eventType": "test",
  "data": { "hello": "world" }
}
